	"d2P1oIJ,D4 mode,OS/Stock,PBI,HSIO;",
	"P1-;",
	"P1OAC,SIO drive speed,Standard,Fast-6,Fast-5,Fast-4,Fast-3,Fast-2,Fast-1,Fast-0;",
